WEBVTT

03:54.860 --> 04:03.100
Yesterday, we have had a nice meditation,
and we all felt the cool breeze of the Holy

04:03.109 --> 04:18.540
Ghost, and I told you that we have to understand
that this is the greatest moment in the history,

04:18.540 --> 04:30.380
while you are born, and you are doing the
highest work, that is of God, here. And you

04:30.380 --> 04:40.000
are specially chosen for it and how you must
know that you are a saint.

04:40.000 --> 04:46.500
Apart from this, all the blessings that you
have, you also get lost sometimes in your

04:46.500 --> 04:56.070
blessings and start behaving in a manner which
doesn’t behove a saintly person. Now after

04:56.070 --> 05:10.840
so many years I have agreed or I agreed to
have Ekadesha Rudra Puja, which was, I know

05:10.840 --> 05:15.110
was a dangerous thing to do because I know
still so many Sahaja Yogis are half-baked,

05:15.110 --> 05:20.970
some are just taking advantage of Sahaja Yoga,
and making money out of it or getting some

05:20.970 --> 05:28.100
power out of it, or fame, or something.
So this was let loose now, this power, and

05:28.100 --> 05:34.270
is a very, very dangerous power in a way,
and you have to be very careful. It of course

05:34.270 --> 05:40.210
protects you from the people who attack you
and try to destroy you from all negativity.

05:40.210 --> 05:47.380
It wants to work out all kinds of protection
that is possible for you, but if you start

05:47.380 --> 05:53.450
misbehaving, also it can act upon you.
I’ll give you a story about something happened

05:53.450 --> 06:04.370
very recently in India. One Sahaja Yogi went
to another Sahaja Yogi’s place, who had

06:04.370 --> 06:10.870
lots of jackfruits in her garden. And she
said, “Why don’t you give me one jackfruit

06:10.870 --> 06:15.020
because I want to make some vegetable out
of it.” So she said, “Not today. I’ll

06:15.020 --> 06:21.550
give you some other day; I don’t want to
give you today.” That’s all. And she had

06:21.550 --> 06:27.470
lots of jackfruits. So the Sahaja Yogi felt
bad, that you see, she just wanted to make

06:27.470 --> 06:33.330
some vegetables for some nice people coming
to her house. Costs you nothing in the market,

06:33.330 --> 06:39.900
just she liked the jackfruit so she said “Can
I have one jackfruit?” Next day there was

06:39.900 --> 06:49.630
a very big wind, a kind of a typhoon came,
only in her garden, nowhere else. And all

06:49.630 --> 06:57.220
her jackfruits fell down. Also, the tree fell
down. And she didn’t know what to do so

06:57.220 --> 07:03.120
she came back and she said to this, another
Sahaja Yogini, “I’m sorry I’ve said

07:03.120 --> 07:10.800
these things. That is what has happened. Now
you please save me from another disaster because

07:10.800 --> 07:18.840
I have been rather selfish towards myself.”
She said, “No, I never said anything to

07:18.840 --> 07:22.990
Mother. I never told Her. I just came back
home, I forgot everything. I never told anything

07:22.990 --> 07:31.770
to Mother. I never carried any malice in my
mind. I was absolutely very forgiving. How

07:31.770 --> 07:39.110
it has happened?” This has happened after
the Ekadesha Rudra Puja and she was worried

07:39.110 --> 07:44.960
that all her garden will be swept away one
day. So she wrote a letter to Me saying, Mother,

07:44.960 --> 07:50.930
this is what has happened. I have done it
because I have these bad habits from my past

07:50.930 --> 08:00.740
life, and I tried to save one jackfruit and
then she had to give it away to beggars, to

08:00.740 --> 08:08.320
servants. Nobody would buy those jackfruits
from her. Then she lost all her money. She

08:08.320 --> 08:14.830
lost everything.
I know it is rather dangerous but how to destroy

08:14.830 --> 08:21.830
the negativity? And today I find the negativity
is also hurting Sahaja Yoga, very much, and

08:21.830 --> 08:27.240
Sahaja Yogis. Through a very subtle method.
As you must have heard about Australia, what

08:27.240 --> 08:35.449
has happened there. One lady who was sent
from her husband to Australia to get corrected.

08:35.449 --> 08:41.469
So there’s another one who’s a wife of
someone. She’s very conscious of her “wifeness.”

08:41.469 --> 08:50.720
She got hold of this negative woman and created
a group of negative such women. And all the

08:50.720 --> 08:56.829
vibrations of Sahaja Yoga were finished there.
On My birthday, not one person sent Me even

08:56.829 --> 09:05.819
a flower from Australia. They did my puja,
all right. That ritual they did, puja. But

09:05.819 --> 09:12.709
families. She said that we are doing in our
own family. Which is your family? This small

09:12.709 --> 09:20.740
little family of ashram, or your own family?
And the whole thing got destroyed. All the

09:20.740 --> 09:28.949
vibrations of all the Australians was destroyed.
Then I had to call the leader to Bombay. He

09:28.949 --> 09:33.759
was so upset with his own vibrations because
started shaking before me. His hands started

09:33.759 --> 09:41.079
trembling before me. He said, “I am sensitive.”
I said, “No, this is bhoot, this is not

09:41.079 --> 09:44.829
sensitivity. If you get anything, pains, or
anything like that, that means you’re a

09:44.829 --> 09:49.410
bhoot. You’re not sensitive. Don’t be
diverted. Don’t think like that. Don’t

09:49.410 --> 09:55.009
have wrong ideas about yourself.” I said,
“You sit down before me now.” Then I took

09:55.009 --> 10:01.930
out the spirits from him. Then he admitted
there was an “Assault of Scottish people

10:01.930 --> 10:06.980
on me, Scottish people”. Why? Because she
went from Scotland. I said, “Bhoots do not

10:06.980 --> 10:12.329
have any nationality. They do not have any
cast. They don’t have any religion. They

10:12.329 --> 10:18.180
are bhoots. So don’t call them Scottish.
They could be Russians. They could be Italians.

10:18.180 --> 10:23.899
They could be Indians. They could be anything.”
But such a lot them that the whole of Australia,

10:23.899 --> 10:30.660
the whole of New York got caught up.
So how the negativity crawls into it and a

10:30.660 --> 10:37.899
person like James who is a saint was hurt.
Not hurt but he was absolutely ruined and

10:37.899 --> 10:43.110
he admitted that Mother, I know what has happened.
But I found out his wife who was guilty. She

10:43.110 --> 10:48.649
had a very bad past. Allergic to things. [SHE
WAS…del] All kinds of things she had. I

10:48.649 --> 10:56.689
told her that you have to get out of Australia.
So the Maha puja has been postponed in a way.

10:56.689 --> 11:01.370
I’ll see to it that we do it but may not
be any one of the Sahaja Yogis from that ashram

11:01.370 --> 11:09.110
come. And then to my surprise, all these horrible
six women who had formed a group with this

11:09.110 --> 11:15.850
woman, wrote a letter to me that “She has
uplifted us.” And the vibrations were so

11:15.850 --> 11:21.089
bad that I just felt the whole vibrations
started flowing and fighting with them. I

11:21.089 --> 11:26.800
couldn’t read the letter. And they felt
they have been uplifted. So in Sahaja Yoga,

11:26.800 --> 11:34.730
you can be misled very much by so many things.
But now, be careful. Don’t try to cheat

11:34.730 --> 11:40.790
yourself. Must understand your own value.
As I told you yesterday that you are yogis,

11:40.790 --> 11:46.579
you are saints, and you should not yield to
anything nonsensical and cheapish. Anybody

11:46.579 --> 11:49.839
who tries to do all those things, you should
tell them “You are yogis.”

11:49.839 --> 11:57.329
As I told you yesterday that for a person
who is a yogi, [HINDI phrase] the whole world

11:57.329 --> 12:04.709
is his own family. Specially it is very much
in Europe, I find, and England and America.

12:04.709 --> 12:10.509
The women have become very dominant. And they
know how to control men by telling them stories

12:10.509 --> 12:17.850
about how to look after the family, how to
look after the children, how to do that. Sometimes

12:17.850 --> 12:27.790
it’s amazing. And you get lost with it.
I have seen so many of like that. It has created

12:27.790 --> 12:33.399
so many problems. Now I request all the women
to behave themselves and understand they are

12:33.399 --> 12:37.600
wives. And whatever blessings they have got
from Sahaja Yoga will be all withdrawn if

12:37.600 --> 12:43.249
you start misbehaving. And all kinds of miseries
will be upon them, not because of Me but because

12:43.249 --> 12:50.199
of Ekadesha Rudra. As you put everything on
the bhoots, let Me put it on all the deities.

12:50.199 --> 12:54.399
I don’t take any responsibility. Because
if you are irresponsible, they’ll hit you

12:54.399 --> 13:00.540
hard and you will end up with cancer or something
very serious and then, don’t blame me. This

13:00.540 --> 13:07.069
is the situation today. I have known some
Sahaja Yoginis who confessed to me that they

13:07.069 --> 13:13.319
have been doing this, they have been doing
that. They have been talking about families–this,

13:13.319 --> 13:20.220
that. And they have been hurt. This is to
be understood because I think the women in

13:20.220 --> 13:26.059
the West do not have intelligence. They are
not intelligent. That’s the simple equation

13:26.059 --> 13:30.470
I have reached. Some have intelligence and
even if they are caught up they are sensible,

13:30.470 --> 13:35.939
if they are intelligent. But the women here
are aggressive but not intelligent. An intelligent

13:35.939 --> 13:43.100
woman is in India. She sees the point. She
knows this is Adi Shakti. If her husband is

13:43.100 --> 13:48.319
doing something wrong she’ll just say “I’ll
fast for ten days. Will you behave yourself?”

13:48.319 --> 13:56.059
“Or, I’ll get out of this house if you
don’t behave yourself.” Is the women In

13:56.059 --> 14:01.369
India who have made Sahaja Yoga successful
in India; the very intelligent women. Here

14:01.369 --> 14:07.009
the women lack intelligence because they are
so aggressive. They do not see the point.

14:07.009 --> 14:14.779
They do not understand who I am. They do not
understand, what is our worth. To them all

14:14.779 --> 14:20.860
nonsensical stupid things are important. Not
all of you but some of you. And because the

14:20.860 --> 14:27.819
intelligence is less, you yield to such women
who are stupid. They tell you all kinds of

14:27.819 --> 14:34.540
things. They talk well. Here only the women
talk, I have seen. Men do not talk. If you

14:34.540 --> 14:40.329
see a television, only the women are talking.
Men never talk. A child has died, it is the

14:40.329 --> 14:43.619
mother who is talking. I don’t know how
she can talk when her child is dead. She’s

14:43.619 --> 14:49.160
the one who will talk. And the father will
be unhappy, like a mouse sitting there, keeping

14:49.160 --> 14:53.920
shut. So many times I have told Sahaja Yogis
in England and elsewhere that you are like

14:53.920 --> 14:59.189
cabbages. If you behave like this, the day
will come when you all will be destroyed by

14:59.189 --> 15:04.029
these horrible women.
Now women have to understand they are women

15:04.029 --> 15:11.600
because they are compassionate, they are forbearing.
They are like this Mother Earth. Their ego

15:11.600 --> 15:18.399
is so developed. Be careful about it. Why
America is finished today? Because of their

15:18.399 --> 15:23.160
women. I can give you so many examples of
Indian girls who are married here. They brought

15:23.160 --> 15:28.790
round their husbands. They put everything
right. They have slowly and steadily put them

15:28.790 --> 15:35.699
properly into Sahaja Yoga. This is a very
common failing of the West and I don’t know

15:35.699 --> 15:42.369
what has happened to the men here. They feel
so guilty that they must become like slaves.

15:42.369 --> 15:46.899
Is the other way around in India quite a lot
in the North India, I should say, that women

15:46.899 --> 15:51.610
are very much dominated. We had one Sahaja
Yogini. Her husband was a Sahaja Yogi, he

15:51.610 --> 15:57.589
was a doctor. He got paralysis. When he got
paralysis, his wife started earning money.

15:57.589 --> 16:05.550
When she started earning money, he felt very
humiliated. Then he dominated her much more.

16:05.550 --> 16:09.410
She came and told me, “It was nice when
I was not earning — he was much sweeter

16:09.410 --> 16:16.129
to me…now I’m earning…” And she was
giving every single pie to him. Still he was

16:16.129 --> 16:20.529
dominating her all the time. “Why you didn’t
do this? Why you didn’t do that?” She

16:20.529 --> 16:25.329
said, “Never did that before. As soon as
he’s all right, I’m going to give up my

16:25.329 --> 16:31.429
earnings,” she said, “because my husband
cannot stand my earnings.”

16:31.429 --> 16:36.220
So I have to request you people, first and
foremost thing, all the Sahaja Yoginis must

16:36.220 --> 16:43.189
know Sahaja Yoga as well as the men know.
Not just smiling and dressing up is important.

16:43.189 --> 16:50.290
In Sahaja Yoga, you must have the same knowledge
as any Sahaja Yogi has. If you have produced

16:50.290 --> 16:54.589
children it doesn’t mean that you have achieved
something great. Anybody can produce children:

16:54.589 --> 17:04.069
dogs, cats, everyone. Also your husbands are
responsible partly for it. So nothing you

17:04.069 --> 17:08.000
have achieved great by producing children,
looking after the children, dominating your

17:08.000 --> 17:14.029
husband all the time. How much do you know
about Sahaja Yoga? I know some of them do

17:14.029 --> 17:20.630
not know what are the chakras on the feet.
They don’t want to know anything about Sahaja

17:20.630 --> 17:26.240
Yoga. Only they want to use Sahaja Yoga sometimes
to dominate the husbands. One has to face

17:26.240 --> 17:36.090
it up. How much do you know deeply about Sahaja
Yoga? Most of you have so many problems within

17:36.090 --> 17:40.740
yourselves. As I have seen, some of you, as
soon as you put hands towards someone, you

17:40.740 --> 17:46.250
feel, “Oh, here, I’m catching here.”
That’s the sign of a regular bhoot in you.

17:46.250 --> 17:53.450
And I have seen people saying that they are
sensitive. It’s such a misleading thing.

17:53.450 --> 17:59.059
“I am very sensitive. I am very much higher
in Sahaja Yoga.” That’s not the way you

17:59.059 --> 18:06.799
are going to be higher. You have to be absolutely
perfect, in perfect health and perfect knowledge

18:06.799 --> 18:12.730
about Sahaja Yoga you should have. How many
of you have read Advent? Let us see. How many

18:12.730 --> 18:30.039
of you have read full Advent? Alright. That’s
good. How many English girls have read Advent?

18:30.039 --> 18:39.159
Honestly. Honestly. That’s good.
Now, what I’m trying to say that you have

18:39.159 --> 18:52.840
to find out, what is Sahaja Yoga? Your Guru
is a woman. She is the source of all the knowledge.

18:52.840 --> 18:58.380
She is the Ocean of All the Knowledge. And
why should we lag behind? In all things we

18:58.380 --> 19:05.260
want to be absolutely equal, similar to men.
Even in dressing up and everything. And what

19:05.260 --> 19:14.190
about in knowledge about Sahaja Yoga? How
many have given realizations to others? Raise

19:14.190 --> 19:25.010
your hands. Only the women I am interested
in. That’s good. So that is what one should

19:25.010 --> 19:35.559
be proud of. One should know how much you
know Sahaja Yoga mentally, emotionally. How

19:35.559 --> 19:44.090
many of you dominate your husband? Be careful.
She is the only honest person, I think. I

19:44.090 --> 19:52.380
know all of you who dominate. And try to crush
them also, sometimes. I’m requesting you

19:52.380 --> 19:58.340
now because you are the shakti. You are the
power behind the man. You are the one who

19:58.340 --> 20:05.429
are going to make them great. You are the
one who are going to build up Sahaja Yoga

20:05.429 --> 20:12.220
as a potential energy. You are like this Mother
Earth who has to give everything beautiful–all

20:12.220 --> 20:20.830
these flowers. From where do they come? All
these trees. This Mother Earth looks so simple.

20:20.830 --> 20:31.470
But what She gives us, look at that. Look
at those beautiful things. So one has to understand

20:31.470 --> 20:38.720
that to be a good Sahaja Yogini, first of
all you have to be an excellent wife. And

20:38.720 --> 20:45.600
not a dominating wife, pushing yourself forward
all the time. I have realized this very much,

20:45.600 --> 20:49.850
but now recently I have got 3 – 4 cases
in which I’m really shocked the way things

20:49.850 --> 20:58.889
are happening. And they can hit at me or hit
at the leaders, hit at anyone. Because it’s

20:58.889 --> 21:06.539
easy for bhoots to get the women than the
men. Is true. When you go too much towards

21:06.539 --> 21:13.350
the right, you immediately get caught up on
the left because you move like a swing, because

21:13.350 --> 21:19.700
naturally you are the left-sided thing, and
then the bhoots catch you much more than they

21:19.700 --> 21:25.720
catch other people.
You’ll be amazed that when I see the women

21:25.720 --> 21:31.620
who have led a perverted sex life are much
worse than men. After marriage, men get cured,

21:31.620 --> 21:36.669
women do not. They have mental problems because
you must know you are the emotions, you are

21:36.669 --> 21:42.570
the desires of the whole world. You are so
important without you nothing can start. If

21:42.570 --> 21:50.090
I had not come on this Earth, put all of them
together, right from Sadashiva to Ganesha,

21:50.090 --> 21:58.899
they could not have done anything. It is a
fact. It’s Me as a Woman, as a Mother, as

21:58.899 --> 22:10.110
a Wife, as the Spouse has achieved this. And
that’s what for you, it should be the easiest

22:10.110 --> 22:15.940
thing to do because I’m a Woman and I’ve
lived like a Woman and I’ve managed so many

22:15.940 --> 22:22.460
children all over the world. Managed the whole
show, managed My family also very well. I

22:22.460 --> 22:34.029
balanced it very well. And how it is now proved
that a woman can not only be a priest but

22:34.029 --> 22:42.690
she can be the highest Guru of gurus. I put
all of you on the pedestal now. So I have

22:42.690 --> 22:53.309
to tell you that you have to come up and you
have to look after your Sahaja. You are very

22:53.309 --> 23:00.970
important because a bad woman and a bad wife
is very much more detrimental than a bad man.

23:00.970 --> 23:08.559
I have seen now in Australia happening. One
woman has ruined the whole of Australia and

23:08.559 --> 23:22.080
one woman can make the whole of Australia
a great thing. That’s Me. I’m very proud

23:22.080 --> 23:40.769
to be a woman and I would hate to be a man.
Look at Shri Krishna. He had to marry 16,000

23:40.769 --> 23:48.179
women. He had to marry them. He could not
have them as disciples. They were shaktis,

23:48.179 --> 23:54.269
they were His powers. They had to be women.
They would have said, already they are saying,

23:54.269 --> 24:03.179
that He was a ladies’ man. But to Me nobody
can say that, because I am a woman and a mother

24:03.179 --> 24:11.279
is not challenged. Father is always challenged.
Not the mother. So many things you can achieve

24:11.279 --> 24:16.700
as a woman.
For that you have to know few things. How

24:16.700 --> 24:31.700
to express your pure love to others. How to
express your genuineness to others. How to

24:31.700 --> 24:42.460
help your husband in Sahaja Yoga. In the marriage
of Sahaja Yoga, you have given a promise to

24:42.460 --> 24:50.250
Me, that you’ll work for Sahaja Yoga and
you’ll help your husband in doing Sahaja

24:50.250 --> 24:58.500
Yoga. You’ll help your husband when he’s
looking after other Sahaja Yogis. And you’ll

24:58.500 --> 25:04.350
look after other Sahaja Yogis who come to
your house. You’ll make your house a Sahaja

25:04.350 --> 25:15.860
Yoga center, receive the people in your house
and will always try to enhance the collectivity.

25:15.860 --> 25:24.500
Under these promises you are married. You
are the one who can show that. It is easy

25:24.500 --> 25:34.120
for a woman to be short-sighted, conceited
and mean. It takes time for man to be that.

25:34.120 --> 25:41.649
But with all these possibilities, even if
you have another possibility of men to dominate,

25:41.649 --> 25:45.130
then you are neither here nor there. You have
no sex, then. I mean, I don’t know what

25:45.130 --> 25:51.779
even to call them then. You better name it,
a person who is neither woman nor a man. Let

25:51.779 --> 26:03.210
us be women and be proud of it. That’s how
we can make a very good world for everyone.

26:03.210 --> 26:08.960
So, now, coming to the major problems of the
world.

26:08.960 --> 26:14.600
We have seen that I am talking about politics
quite a lot these days, and maybe one day

26:14.600 --> 26:20.559
all of you have to enter into politics when
the proper time has come. Also, I’m going

26:20.559 --> 26:29.169
to see this Mr. Jackson in America. Let’s
see what works out. Also, as you know, we

26:29.169 --> 26:38.230
are working it out in England. I am going
to within 2 years time, see all these leaders.

26:38.230 --> 26:46.149
And we are going to work it out in a way that
is sensible, dignified. But it is for you

26:46.149 --> 26:54.299
people to show that you are very balanced,
good families.

