that? Vishna, your son is very mischievous.

27:04.289 --> 27:11.500
Will you please take him away? You must teach
them how to behave before Mother. You must

27:11.500 --> 27:26.879
teach them. One child can spoil all the other
children. Be careful. You must smack them

27:26.879 --> 27:30.850
sometimes, I think it’s necessary. Otherwise
the children can never behave themselves.

27:30.850 --> 27:39.350
