and they are all right.]

27:39.350 --> 27:49.710
We have to build up societies and families,
with proper training, with proper understanding.

27:49.710 --> 27:54.789
We have to treat our children also with the
same understanding. As I told you, till the

27:54.789 --> 28:00.000
age of five years, you can smack them. [AFTER
THE AGE…del] Till the age of ten years,

28:00.000 --> 28:05.169
you should teach them and after the age of
sixteen years, they are to be treated just

28:05.169 --> 28:09.210
like your friends. But first if you have missed
these two points, you can never treat them.

28:09.210 --> 28:18.799
They’ll sit on your head. This is the problem
also of children in this country. But today

28:18.799 --> 28:24.830
the problems are much deeper than what we
think of. A kind of a negative force like

28:24.830 --> 28:33.960
a Hitler’s force is rising up through women
of all the countries. Through women this horrible

28:33.960 --> 28:42.019
Hitler and all these Germans who died are
taking birth. They are becoming [LIKE…del]

28:42.019 --> 28:53.360
now, just like Nazis. So women have to be
very careful not to give way to negative forces

28:53.360 --> 29:01.889
that are working within us. They have to be
humble, they have to be sweet and sacrificing

29:01.889 --> 29:05.909
because they have a power to do it. It’s
only the women who can do it. Not the men.

29:05.909 --> 29:11.710
Men can’t do it. They have other sweetness
about them. Men have some other sweetness

29:11.710 --> 29:20.509
about them. But the women have that intelligence
which can build the whole world into a beautiful

29:20.509 --> 29:25.360
world.
