Yesterday you were not here and they were
all very quiet. Now behave properly. All of

29:42.690 --> 29:48.200
you must learn to behave. All right? You must
teach your children when you bring them here,

29:48.200 --> 29:54.029
or bring anywhere, that how to behave. You
must teach them. You must tell them. Children

29:54.029 --> 30:01.539
must learn.]
Now, so we come to the deeper problems of

30:01.539 --> 30:12.409
this world. Is that the mental projection
has now shown clearly, be with Me, all of

30:12.409 --> 30:20.820
you. Try to understand. Is a very deep problem,
that if you go to the left or to the right

30:20.820 --> 30:29.840
you jump into the extremes, into the problems,
and you create problems. So we have to keep

30:29.840 --> 30:39.269
everybody in the center. And to keeping in
the center, we have to ascend. Now the problem

30:39.269 --> 30:47.529
is that we have many people who have come
to Sahaja Yoga. This was never achieved before,

30:47.529 --> 30:55.330
never achieved before. For that, the main
reason was that it was impossible to penetrate

30:55.330 --> 31:00.549
into the minds of the people, and tell them
what is to be done. Everybody tried their

31:00.549 --> 31:08.179
level best. Today only I was discussing Buddha.
I said Buddha tried his level best to tell

31:08.179 --> 31:15.960
people that they should get out of nonsensical
ritualism, and get to their salvation. He

31:15.960 --> 31:24.499
tried everything. So when He died, they said,
“Alright, he has said not to make any statues;

31:24.499 --> 31:33.899
we’ll make stupas.” So they made stupas
that they started worshipping. Just the opposite

31:33.899 --> 31:43.549
what He said, that just now you get your salvation,
your cleansing, introspection and the middle

31:43.549 --> 31:49.779
path. He even went up to the idea that don’t
have families. With the families means this

31:49.779 --> 31:57.580
nonsense. You just take to renunciation within
yourself so that you see all these things.

31:57.580 --> 32:05.070
But as usual, as they were again consolidated
into their nonsensical things, they made big

32:05.070 --> 32:12.749
stupas and things and worshipped. You see
that in the life of Christ. You see that in

32:12.749 --> 32:19.669
the life of Mahavira. You see that in the
lives of all the great incarnations and prophets,

32:19.669 --> 32:30.159
Islam and everything. Same thing has happened,
that they have perverted it. But who has perverted?

32:30.159 --> 32:43.700
Who has spoiled the whole essence of every
great incarnation? It was spoiled by the disciples

32:43.700 --> 32:52.379
themselves because they were not realized.
Now, the deep problem I find is the women

32:52.379 --> 32:58.600
who are supposed to be My disciples will be
spoiling Sahaja Yoga . Very clearly I can

32:58.600 --> 33:06.379
see it now. I can see it so clearly, absolutely
clearly. They are going to spoil because they

33:06.379 --> 33:13.450
have become very dominating. Because they
think they know Sahaja Yoga. Because they

33:13.450 --> 33:20.940
think they have become very great. A leader’s
wife thinks she’s the leader herself. If

33:20.940 --> 33:25.129
you call somebody that “All right, come
and do this job for Me,” the wife thinks

33:25.129 --> 33:34.159
she has a right on her husband more than Mother
has. Is the women who are the culprit today

33:34.159 --> 33:39.960
and that’s why I want to warn you. Now I
have seen it. I can point it out, at least

33:39.960 --> 33:51.370
ten women like that who have done it. And
now the eleventh. It’s just here. This is

33:51.370 --> 33:56.009
what it is.
And I have to request you to understand that

33:56.009 --> 34:01.990
the responsibility will be on you. When it
will be written down in history, where, as

34:01.990 --> 34:09.649
Ramayana was written, it was the maid servant
of Kaikai, the mother, the stepmother of Rama,

34:09.649 --> 34:17.059
is the one who is responsible for the whole
of thing that happened in the Ramayana. But

34:17.059 --> 34:25.649
that was to happen. But where is that Manthara
today, and where is that Kaikai? [THAT…del]

34:25.649 --> 34:33.599
Indians do not take their names. They spit
if anybody takes that name. To the dogs they

34:33.599 --> 34:39.730
have gone. They thought that time they have
achieved a lot. This is what I have to tell

34:39.730 --> 34:46.260
you. If you want to go like that, down in
the history, because this is a very precarious

34:46.260 --> 34:52.819
time we are facing, and we have to be very,
very careful about ourselves. What are we

34:52.819 --> 35:00.710
up to? What are we doing? I deal with the
present moment and the present times. And

35:00.710 --> 35:06.960
I don’t want to say what will happen to
you in future. If you have to go to hell,

35:06.960 --> 35:11.619
you can go. I’m not going to say who’s
going to go to hell and who’s going to go

35:11.619 --> 35:17.079
to heavens, but it is for you to decide through
your introspection, to understand what’s

35:17.079 --> 35:25.240
going to happen. And I have to specially make
a very important request to the women that

35:25.240 --> 35:29.540
in these modern times, they are the ones who
are going to save the world. Not the men.

35:29.540 --> 35:35.690
They have done their job before. Now it is
for you to save, with your understanding,

35:35.690 --> 35:41.839
with your compassion, with your sacrifices,
with your wisdom and the innate love, not

35:41.839 --> 35:51.200
only your children, your husband, your family,
but the whole world. It is a very good opportunity

35:51.200 --> 36:02.930
for all of you to do your bit. It has been
a tremendous experience with some of the very

36:02.930 --> 36:12.800
great Sahaja Yoginis we have. Some of them
have achieved, really, as you can say, the

36:12.800 --> 36:25.630
constant state of bliss. Really. Some of them
have. In the constant state of bliss. Even

36:25.630 --> 36:32.359
if they are coming, immediately I can feel
they are coming. The whole atmosphere waits

36:32.359 --> 36:46.349
for them. The whole cosmos, just in complete
respectful attendance, is waiting for their

36:46.349 --> 36:53.559
arrival. There are women of that quality.
And we have to take them as ideals, and not

36:53.559 --> 37:01.680
the stupid, useless, vain women. We have to
take them as something great.

37:01.680 --> 37:07.430
This is what I have to tell you that the potential
within you is very great. Sahaja Yoga should

37:07.430 --> 37:25.800
not be limited to you or to your children.
So the depth that you have, you touch. The

37:25.800 --> 37:33.000
problem of today, that the women have lost
their values, they have lost their depth.

37:33.000 --> 37:41.579
This is the basic problem of today. They have
become competitive, money oriented, success

37:41.579 --> 37:51.319
oriented, all nonsensical things. They are
not ascent oriented. So you have to be very,

37:51.319 --> 37:57.270
very careful. Basically this is the problem
you should see and I would request all the

37:57.270 --> 38:04.819
Sahaja Yogis to be on the watch. The same
woman today can be ladder to the heaven or

38:04.819 --> 38:17.170
could be a slide downward. Somehow they have
achieved that kind of a position, now, that

38:17.170 --> 38:23.740
they can dictate, just like Hitler. Took only
eleven years. I think these women have taken,

38:23.740 --> 38:33.119
I don’t know how many years, but now I see
them on the scene. A woman without righteousness,

38:33.119 --> 38:43.890
a woman without chastity, a woman without
humility is not a woman. Compassion is her

38:43.890 --> 38:59.050
decoration. I wish I could write like William
Blake. I wish he had written about the women

38:59.050 --> 39:15.250
of the west and the beauty that they were.
And that they have to achieve. Once the women

39:15.250 --> 39:24.079
really know their strength, they will make
this world a beautiful one, I know that. But

39:24.079 --> 39:37.309
not their weaknesses where they fall at the
pattern of men. That’s their weakness.

39:37.309 --> 39:45.630
So, in this program we have been able to achieve
two things. Yesterday I told you about introspection,

39:45.630 --> 39:54.079
and today I have told you where is the problem.
Even if you make a big boat, the biggest boat,

39:54.079 --> 40:02.500
which is seaworthy, and make a big hole in
it, that boat will be sunk. Even if you have

40:02.500 --> 40:14.480
the brightest eyes, but a little hole goes
into your eyes, you can’t see the skies.

40:14.480 --> 40:26.380
And in their subtle method, these women have
the knack to put that in your eyes. And they

40:26.380 --> 40:31.410
have also the knack to open the complete vision
of beauty.

40:31.410 --> 40:37.890
I’m so very happy in India for one reason:
Most of the men come and tell me: “It’s

40:37.890 --> 40:44.690
my wife who brought me to Sahaja Yoga. It
is she who exposed me to Sahaja Yoga. It is

40:44.690 --> 40:50.230
she who’s done so much for me, for Sahaja
Yoga.” And such tremendous respect for the

40:50.230 --> 40:58.380
women. Even those who have come here, I’ve
seen some of them, have slowly and steadily

40:58.380 --> 41:06.690
brought their husbands to Sahaja Yoga. Of
course Indians also have some horrid women,

41:06.690 --> 41:12.119
and when they come abroad, if they are westernized,
and are exposed to western life, also they

41:12.119 --> 41:21.740
can be very horrid too.
But innately, a women’s attitude in India

41:21.740 --> 41:28.270
is different, that she has to establish the
dharma in her family. She has to establish

41:28.270 --> 41:36.430
the beauty of God in her family. She has to
give all that is good to her children, all

41:36.430 --> 41:41.309
righteousness. She has to be humble. She has
not to raise her voice. If she raises her

41:41.309 --> 41:46.970
voice, then she spoils her children: she teaches
them how to raise the voice. She has to, in

41:46.970 --> 41:54.180
a way, obey her husband because children should
obey her. It works; the society is much better

41:54.180 --> 42:03.280
there than it is here. So this new, also,
a movement of women’s lib and all that,

42:03.280 --> 42:17.400
is a sign of that
secret work that is going on. Because women
are left-sided, they are sly. They work it

42:17.400 --> 42:32.599
out very cleverly and cunningly. But you all
could be like Me. You all could achieve all

42:32.599 --> 42:39.309
My powers much more than men can achieve if
you want to. But you have to get out of your

42:39.309 --> 42:51.490
small visions and small ideas about glorifying
yourself. I’m sure it will work out if you

42:51.490 --> 42:58.040
take it upon yourself that we all could do
what Mother is doing today.

42:58.040 --> 43:08.839
First thing you must learn to cook well. Don’t
allow men to do any work in the household.

43:08.839 --> 43:17.890
Never. Never allow your husband to do any
work in the household. They will just entirely

43:17.890 --> 43:28.500
depend on you. Make the best food. Be an expert
cook. The husband will be back home. I’m

43:28.500 --> 43:42.680
giving you the tricks of the trade. Try to
understand your husband like a witness. Sometimes

43:42.680 --> 43:48.829
he gets angry for nothing at all and all that.
Be a witness to that. He is another child

43:48.829 --> 43:58.099
you have. It’s a grown up child and you
have to look after a grown up child. Be kind

43:58.099 --> 44:11.319
and attentive. It is very surprising that
you all have not yet learnt those tricks.

44:11.319 --> 44:48.089
Perhaps your mothers never told you.
We are going to be a very ideal race, an ideal

44:48.089 --> 44:54.170
family, an ideal everything, no doubt. We
are going to show to the world, whatever people

44:54.170 --> 45:01.720
may try tricks on us, we are not bothered.
We have to go further and further. Like Ganesha

45:01.720 --> 45:09.390
you can say, a huge big elephant tied with
all kinds of ropes and all kinds of chains

45:09.390 --> 45:23.430
can go and push forward. In this manner, we
all Sahaja Yogis are going to work it out.

45:23.430 --> 45:31.260
But the ladies of Sahaja Yoga have to work
it out. They have to see that they give that

45:31.260 --> 45:38.890
power to their men. If I find any husband
weak, I know it’s the wife who is a nagger

45:38.890 --> 45:53.290
or who is a dominating person, or who thinks
no end of herself. And if I see a man so powerful,

45:53.290 --> 46:07.920
I know there’s a woman behind him. It’s
just like electricity and a light and a lamp.

46:07.920 --> 46:15.410
If the electricity is flowing alright, the
lamp is burning. Absolutely that. But if you

46:15.410 --> 46:25.900
are identified with these stupid vain women,
then you are lost. You’ll be finished. If

46:25.900 --> 46:33.549
you know what I am, if you know what I am
saying, and if you try to follow what you

46:33.549 --> 46:51.910
have to do, then you will immediately see
that Mother is trying to strengthen our roots.

46:51.910 --> 47:01.359
Because you are the roots of the trees. You
have to give all the nourishment. You have

47:01.359 --> 47:13.470
to be motherly, sisterly towards all the other
Sahaja Yogis. Not to quarrel, to fight, to

47:13.470 --> 47:30.670
say hard things. That’s not the job of a
woman. Not to argue but be quiet and watch

47:30.670 --> 47:37.400
out. Even if they are catching on certain
chakras, you can cleanse them very well as

47:37.400 --> 47:45.069
wives. You can work it out secretly. You can
do it. Because the problem, though it looks

47:45.069 --> 47:55.960
so dangerous, and so destructive and shocking,
the keys are in the hands of the women of

47:55.960 --> 48:06.289
today. They can just solve the problem like
that if they decide and understand their glory

48:06.289 --> 48:20.799
and their value, and do not make themselves
cheap, hankering after cheap popularity.

48:20.799 --> 48:38.049
If I have been able to nail down this great
problem to a very precise source of it, and

48:38.049 --> 48:44.930
if you can manage the source, I’m sure we
can manage Sahaja Yoga. We can manage the

48:44.930 --> 48:58.800
whole world and the humanity at large is going
to be absolutely saved as that is your desire.
May God bless you
